Introduction
============

This projects contains plugins for Prosody jabber server that are specific
for Sugar usage.

Plugins
=======

Plugins are tested agains Prosody 0.8.2 release.

mod_sugar_muc
-------------
The only difference in comparing with original `muc` plugin is workaround for
https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=37897 issue. This plugin should
be used instead of `muc` until issue will be fixed in `telepathy-gabble` or in
`Prosody`.

mod_sugar_roster
----------------
Provides global roster when anyone see all registered accounts.

Configuration
=============

See http://git.sugarlabs.org/server/base/blobs/master/etc/000.base/prosody.d/.

